BY MS. MOE: Q. Where did you go when you moved away from New York City in October of '99? A. Los Angeles, California. Q. Why did you move to Los Angeles? A. Because I got a job on a TV show. Q. Jane, can you tell the jury what kind of work do you do now? A. I am grateful to still be a working actor. Q. For how many years have you been employed as an actor? A. Twenty-two years. Q. After you moved to California, did you stay in touch with Epstein and Maxwell? A. Yes. Q. For about how many years? A. Until approximately the end of 2002. Q. Approximately how old were you during that year? A. Twenty-two. Q. During the year that you were -- withdrawn. After you moved away, did you continue to travel with Maxwell and Epstein? A. With Epstein for sure. Q. When you traveled with Epstein in your early twenties, did you travel in his private jet? A. Yes.
